### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Get All Recipes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/recipes

### Search Recipes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/recipes?search=pasta

### Get Recipe by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/recipes/123

### Create Recipe
POST http://localhost:3000/api/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spaghetti Carbonara",
  "ingredients": ["spaghetti", "eggs", "bacon", "parmesan"],
  "instructions": "Cook spaghetti. Mix eggs with cheese. Add bacon. Combine everything.",
  "imageDataUrl": ""
}

### Update Recipe
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/recipes/123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Recipe Title",
  "instructions": "Updated instructions"
}

### Delete Recipe
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/recipes/123

